                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870523-22-off113 t17870523-22-cd114"></join> last, two sheets, value 5 s. two<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178705230037"></xptr>pillow-cases, value 2 s. two blankets, value 3 s. two flat irons, value 2 d. one cotton counterpane, value 4 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17870523-22-victim277" type="victimName">
