                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870523-22-defend275 t17870523-22-punish117"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. ROSE.</p>
